#compdef decker
# Documentation: https://github.com/JohnEarnest/Decker
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# Zsh completion for decker multimedia presentation compiler (HyperCard-like)
# Upstream README does not document a stable CLI flag set; the binary loads a
# .deck file by path. Provide file completion only.

_arguments -s -S \
  '*:decker document:_files -g "*.deck"'
